original_title: An Intimate Dinner in Celebration of Warner Bros. Silver Jubilee
overview: Mr. and Mrs. Warner Bros. Pictures and their precocious offspring, Little Miss Vitaphone, host a dinner in honor of Warner Bros. Silver Jubilee, attended by most of the major players and song writers under contract to WB at that time.
title: An Intimate Dinner in Celebration of Warner Bros. Silver Jubilee
